<div class="vhs-page position-relative">
  <div class="vhs-page__grain" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="vhs-page__fog" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <section class="container py-5 vhs-hero">
    <div class="row g-5 align-items-center">
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <span class="vhs-tag">Survival Horror</span>
        <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold vhs-title">VHS</h1>
        <p class="lead vhs-intro">Record. Reveal. Run.</p>
        <p class="vhs-copy">
          Walk the empty streets of Stillwater with a temperamental camcorder as your guide. Static peels back reality and shows what stalks the town when the tape distorts.
        </p>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-3 mt-4">
          <%= link_to 'View Gameplay Shots', '#vhs-gallery', class: 'btn vhs-secondary' %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 text-center">
        <div class="vhs-hero__frame mx-auto">
          <%= image_tag 'VHS_PS2.png', alt: 'CRT television glowing beside a PlayStation 2 and VHS tapes', class: 'img-fluid vhs-hero__image' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="vhs-gallery" class="container pb-5 vhs-gallery">
    <div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
      <div class="col-auto">
        <h2 class="h3 mb-0">Gameplay Glimpses</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-auto">
        <span class="vhs-gallery__note">Captured straight from the camcorder feed</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <figure class="vhs-screenshot-card">
          <div class="ratio ratio-4x3 vhs-screenshot-frame">
            <%= image_tag 'VHS_IMG_1_ONLY_GAMEPLAY_FINAL.png', alt: 'Player exploring a fog drenched street', class: 'vhs-screenshot' %>
          </div>
          <figcaption>Static reveals the outline of something stalking the streets.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <figure class="vhs-screenshot-card">
          <div class="ratio ratio-4x3 vhs-screenshot-frame">
            <%= image_tag 'VHS_IMG_3_ONLY_GAMEPLAY_FINAL.png', alt: 'Player aiming the camcorder down a haunted corridor', class: 'vhs-screenshot' %>
          </div>
          <figcaption>Use the lens to cut through the static and chart a way forward.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <figure class="vhs-screenshot-card">
          <div class="ratio ratio-4x3 vhs-screenshot-frame">
            <%= image_tag 'VHS_IMG_8_ONLY_GAMEPLAY_FINAL.png', alt: 'Static drenched figure looming at the end of a corridor', class: 'vhs-screenshot' %>
          </div>
          <figcaption>Keep movingâ€”when the tape stops, the horrors step through.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
